# OWNERS — Pipelines as Code (PaC) authorization
#
# PaC (running in the op1st-pipelines namespace) reads this Prow-style file
# from the DEFAULT branch to decide who may trigger a PipelineRun on a
# pull_request without a maintainer commenting `/ok-to-test`.
#
# In PaC, `approvers` and `reviewers` have EQUAL power to trigger CI; only the
# `.*` (root) scope is honored. Bot accounts are listed explicitly because the
# GitHub-bot auto-exemption does not apply on Forgejo/Codeberg.
#
# Docs: https://pipelinesascode.com/docs/guide/running/

approvers:
  - goern
  - byteflavour
  - b4mad-renovate
  - op1st-gitops
